Package com.ipt.ebsa.agnostic.client.skyscape.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ConnectionException
    Thrown if a log-in or -out operation fails to complete successfully.
    ControlException
    Thrown if a command operation, such as power on, restart, fails to complete successfully.
    EnvironmentOverrideException
    Thrown if an XPath substitution operation fails to complete successfully.
    InvalidStrategyException
    Thrown if a strategy is being used and something is found which means that the strategy cannot be carried out.
    StrategyFailureException
    Thrown if a strategy is being used and something is found which means that the strategy cannot be carried out.
    UnresolvedDependencyException
    Thrown if a dependency of an entity cannot be resolved.
